****How to depoly Local Repository to GitHub Repository***

1) Install Git using "git-scm.com"

2) Right Click the local repository goto "Gitbase Here"

=========> Command of Git

3) git init (for making local folder into repository)

4) git status (for checking status {files})

5) git add -A (for making files trackable {watch})

6) git config --global user.name "User name"

7) git config --global user.email "User email"

8) git commit -m "Commit here about the work"

9) git remote add origin (add link)

10) git push -u -f origin master

~~~~~~~~~~~***** Get files from github repository to local ****~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
11) git pull origin
